description:
The investment seeks investment results that correspond generally to the price and yield performance of its underlying index, the IQ Global Resources Index.
 The fund invests at least 80% of its net assets, in the investments included in its underlying index. The underlying index seeks to employ a systematic investment process designed to identify opportunities in markets exhibiting trending or momentum characteristics across commodity asset classes, represented by companies that operate in commodity-specific market segments and whose equity securities trade in developed markets, including the U.S. The fund is non-diversified.
